{"tid":2212653,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【媽媽自強】唐寧後悔年青時未有好好學英文　兩孩之母為子女決心重拾課本：不可以再懶了","createTime":"2020-09-22T03:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T08:57:08.000Z","uid":130626,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0eadbba56c4e5c1c73d3294e82ff257883121aa8","tid":2212653,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T03:50:17.000Z","msg":"靚媽唐寧不時開Live與粉絲會面分享生活點滴，包括她與子女的生活點滴，唐寧最近為自己訂下了新目標──學英文，更會每星期開Live公開做英文練習的過程。<br />\n<br />\n事因唐寧最近貼出9歲兒子的功課，指當中題目有很多連自己也不懂答。她坦言悔恨以前學英文總是半途而廢，因此計劃每星期開一次做英交練習的Live，以公開練習過程向自己施壓，以此為鞭策。<br />\n<br />\n唐寧於社交平台貼出兒子的練習，並表示自己有很多題都不懂得回答，因而她決心要好好學習。<br />\n她說：<br />\n&quot;我要為自己做一件事。其實一直以來有一件事我是很希望做到，便是學英文！但總是沒有辦法＂的起心肝＂去學，小時候沒有好好去學，長大後更害怕去學，就算有多少人願意陪著我幫我，只要他們稍一不看着我，我便會逃避去學習，令他們灰心失望。<br />\n現在連仔仔3年級時的練習，也有很多不懂回答。所以我打算一星期在FB開一次做英文練習live，希望以公開練習，來給自己一點壓力。我會從小學4年班練習本開始，希望一星期能升一級，如果大家不怕悶便陪著我學習吧！我不可以再懶了！&quot;<br />\n<br />\n唐寧自8歲起經朋友介紹而成為童星，至今接拍過逾百部影視作品，參演過《戀愛自由式》的游穎、《大唐雙龍傳》的師妃暄以及《天涯俠醫》的夏曉晴等角色深入民心，備受觀眾愛戴。<br />\n<br />\n事業發展順利的唐寧現為兩孩之母，育有9歲兒子俊俊和5歲女兒嗡嗡，同時兼顧家庭和事業的她從不覺吃力，盡力做好演員和媽媽的角色。<br />\n<br />\n放工後的唐寧愛享受家庭樂，除了陪他們一起做功課外，也會與他們齊齊玩音樂和烹飪，十分快樂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2755000/2759148/LeilaKong_thumb_20200922_ch_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2755000%2F2759148%2FLeilaKong_thumb_20200922_ch_1024.jpg&h=20e13db2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2755000/2759148/Leila_1_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2755000%2F2759148%2FLeila_1_1024.jpg&h=024a9d96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 唐寧表示不懂得做兒子的練習。（唐寧IG圖片）"},{"pid":"3a4c191063907dafb240264891e7e9af40ea1610","tid":2212653,"uid":912,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T03:52:54.000Z","msg":"想做佢個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84495553aee93e2720df0cfe94a7f7f4ba7cf0bc","tid":2212653,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T03:53:39.000Z","msg":"運兒子<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60cabe75de9df54955229c443873e8403a4b8996","tid":2212653,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T03:53:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連兒子<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d0651b1385ce8bdb12216fa074100d2f95b032e7","tid":2212653,"uid":167658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T05:04:18.000Z","msg":"媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c553c04e7b16b71b8712f6b578d0c37d974d5cad","tid":2212653,"uid":28913,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T05:10:59.000Z","msg":"我英文幾好, 唔收錢, 呢位太太我可以同你私補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce64193acbad867f8463795acf331819dfe20f17","tid":2212653,"uid":28155,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T05:18:15.000Z","msg":"Downing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c7b0dc7085898d56f536a86c9784d9d1646e07","tid":2212653,"uid":261172,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c553c04e7b16b71b8712f6b578d0c37d974d5cad","tid":2212653,"uid":28913,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T05:10:59.000Z","msg":"我英文幾好, 唔收錢, 呢位太太我可以同你私補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T05:21:35.000Z","msg":"真係唔使錢既野先係最貴既<img src=\"/assets